 client Request ------->server Response ---> DB
  HTTP methods           Response Code
  EX:
  GET                     1xx - Informational messages
  POST                    2xx - OK
  PUT                     3xx - Redirection
  OPTIONS                 4xx - client-side error
  DELETE                  5xx - server-side error
                 Response code
  
